  "detailed_description": "As war plagues The Nine Worlds, mighty Odin faces the biggest challenge of his life - tracking down the soul of his murdered wife.  Champions of Odin is a first-person, action role-playing game set in a visually stunning Norse Mythology universe.  In Champions of Odin, you play as the fearless god Odin, tasked with a gruesome quest into the Norse Underworld to revive the soul of your murdered lover.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nChampions of Odin is being released episodically.  Each episode will take place in 1 of the 9 realms of Norse Mythology.  The first episode takes place in Jotunheim, the land of the giants.",
  "about_the_game": "As war plagues The Nine Worlds, mighty Odin faces the biggest challenge of his life - tracking down the soul of his murdered wife.  Champions of Odin is a first-person, action role-playing game set in a visually stunning Norse Mythology universe.  In Champions of Odin, you play as the fearless god Odin, tasked with a gruesome quest into the Norse Underworld to revive the soul of your murdered lover.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nChampions of Odin is being released episodically.  Each episode will take place in 1 of the 9 realms of Norse Mythology.  The first episode takes place in Jotunheim, the land of the giants.",
